item.description:
The Redline pub in Cambridge is planned for this month's meetup. Website is http://www.redlinecam...

Tentatively I'm scheduling for 8pm. If folks are planning to stay late, there's live music from 10pm-2am by DJ Inkognito, whos playing Funk, Soul, and Disco and some Hip Hop, more info go to the website under entertainment. Hope this will be another great turn out!
item.how_to_find_us: I'll introduce myself this time, and I won't forget to bring my camera!
